    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[AFANTASIA]</strong> is a surreal narrative exploration game about memory, imagination, and who you become when you trade one for the other.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/40d8567d2cd2ccbd10ed6bb1cb7e0a09.poster.avif?t=1766939298\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/40d8567d2cd2ccbd10ed6bb1cb7e0a09.webm?t=1766939298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/40d8567d2cd2ccbd10ed6bb1cb7e0a09.mp4?t=1766939298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up with no past and one certainty: you must leave for the city. A voice  called <strong>Intrusion</strong> serves as your guide in the beautiful small town of <strong>Tempo</strong>—a landscape shaped by your new ability to imagine, and your absence of memories.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Town That Mirrors Your Mind</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every street is a memory layer. Walk through the places that once shaped you and uncover the past you traded away, along with the identity you left behind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/bb95e6233139274857d65f975a60e791.poster.avif?t=1766939298\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/bb95e6233139274857d65f975a60e791.webm?t=1766939298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Point, Imagine, Unlock</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objects are questions. Click a letter, a landslide, a building. Every puzzle reveals what it cost you to imagine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/69961c86ddfe22fd1878e02939209b2d.poster.avif?t=1766939298\" width=600 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/69961c86ddfe22fd1878e02939209b2d.webm?t=1766939298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Live What Others Remember</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evoke playable memories drawn from others, imagined into reality. Each memory brings you closer to the person you used to be, and who you could become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/9dedf3591e554d459e50095df3fccfa0.poster.avif?t=1766939298\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/9dedf3591e554d459e50095df3fccfa0.webm?t=1766939298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remember or Become</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intrusion's hold on you only grows stronger. You must decide whether to reconcile with your origins or embrace an unknown self.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay</strong> in Tempo, or <strong>Leave</strong> for the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/d8fe0592fe425e09c566fd272310d759.webp?t=1766939298\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/f4b46bd8019a630d871617c481615374.poster.avif?t=1766939298\" width=610 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/f4b46bd8019a630d871617c481615374.webm?t=1766939298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/3e6b16e7e060e4574ab635b29f1fadcb.avif?t=1766939298\" width=610 height=175 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336670/extras/d8fe0592fe425e09c566fd272310d759.webp?t=1766939298\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p>",
